-- SFG Australia shares rise after agreeing takeover by IOOF 
-- 
-- Thu May 15, 2014 09:16PM EDT
-- None



SYDNEY, May 16 (Reuters) - Shares in SFG Australia Ltd <SFW.AX> rose as high as 15 percent on Friday after agreeing to a takeover by larger financial services rival IOOF Holdings Ltd <IFL.AX> for about A$670 million ($626.42 million).

The SFG board has unanimously recommended the deal to shareholders.